videos.description: 1H (19:23) KU Devonte' Graham made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Frank Mason III.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham opens scoring with long range 3-pointer

videos.description: 1H (19:04) IND Thomas Bryant made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Indiana answers with 3-pointer from Bryant

videos.description: 1H (16:02) IND Thomas Bryant made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Juwan Morgan.
videos.headline: Bryant knocks down his second 3-pointer of the game

videos.description: Indiana has started the game on-fire from behind the arc as Curtis Jones hits another 3-pointer, the Hoosiers fourth of game.
videos.headline: Indiana keeps hitting from beyond the arc

videos.description: 1H (11:32) KU Josh Jackson made Layup.
videos.headline: Steal leads to first career points for Josh Jackson

videos.description: In a tight back and forth game, James Blackmon Jr. gets loose on the fast break and scores with the foul to level up the score for Indiana.
videos.headline: Blackmon hits tough layup and-1 for Indiana

videos.description: 1H (3:35) KU Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Frank Mason III.
videos.headline: Kansas continues run on Mykhailiuk 3-pointer

videos.description: Thomas Bryant puts on the quick shot fake that allows him to blow by the defender and finish the play with a big two-handed dunk to cut Indiana's deficit to four heading into the half.
videos.headline: Bryant finishes strong half with big dunk for Indiana

videos.description: Kansas head coach Bill Self discusses defending Indiana
videos.headline: Kansas head coach Bill Self discusses defending Indiana

videos.description: 2H (18:44) KU Josh Jackson made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Frank Mason III.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson connects on a 3-pointer

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike sparks Kansas on the defensive end with a mega block that gets the Jayhawks running the other way for a Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk layup.
videos.headline: Azubuike's huge block leads to fast-break points for Kansas

videos.description: 2H (12:23) KU Landen Lucas made Dunk. Assisted by Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk connects with Lucas on alley-oop

videos.description: 2H (10:30) IND Robert Johnson made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Juwan Morgan.
videos.headline: Indiana hits 3-pointer after Lucas loses shoe

videos.description: 2H (8:01) IND James Blackmon Jr. made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Another lead change after another Indiana 3-pointer

videos.description: KU Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk made Dunk. Assisted by Frank Mason III.
videos.headline: Turnover leads to huge Mykhailiuk dunk

videos.description: 2H (6:29) IND Devonte Green made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Green hits the 3-pointer while falling back

videos.description: 2H (4:29) IND James Blackmon Jr. made Layup.
videos.headline: Blackmon Jr. gets the layup and-1 on the baseline

videos.description: KU Frank Mason III made Layup.
videos.headline: Mason III drives to the basket for the layup and-1

videos.description: 2H (2:09) IND James Blackmon Jr. made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Josh Newkirk.
videos.headline: Blackmon Jr. knocks down another 3-pointer for Indiana

videos.description: KU Frank Mason III made Layup.
videos.headline: Mason III with another fastbreak layup and-1

videos.description: KU Frank Mason III made Layup.
videos.headline: Mason III ties the game with one more layup and-1

videos.description: IND James Blackmon Jr. made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Blackmon Jr. hits the 3-pointer in overtime

videos.description: OT (1:46) IND Curtis Jones made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Jones knocks down another one more 3-pointer for Indiana

videos.description: KU Josh Jackson made Two Point Tip Shot.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson comes out of nowhere for putback dunk

videos.description: Holding on to a late lead in overtime, Curtis Jones gets loose and throw down a vicious two-hand dunk to cap off the Indiana win over Kansas.
videos.headline: Jones punctuates Indiana's OT win with huge dunk

videos.description: While his players are having a good time behind him, Indiana head coach Tom Crean feels like it's already March in thrilling OT win over Kansas.
videos.headline: Hoosiers have fun behind Crean

videos.description: Breaking down Indiana's 103-99 overtime win over Kansas
videos.headline: Breaking down Indiana's 103-99 overtime win over Kansas
